                },
                {
                  "id": "p2-e46",
                  "text": "Day 3",
                  "fontSize": 11,
                  "fontName": "MHPMCN\u002BHelveticaNeue-Medium",
                  "color": "#16549D",
                  "boundingBox": {
                    "left": 212.3,
                    "top": 401,
                    "width": 28.3,
                    "height": 7.9
                  },
                  "htmlTag": "",
                  "htmlContainerPath": "",
                  "cssClasses": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": "p2-e47",
                  "text": "Dolmabah\u00E7e Palace is our destination this morning, built by Sultan Abd\u00FCl Mecit in 1856. The extravagant opulence of the palace belies the fact that it was built at a time when the Ottoman Empire was in decline. We then enjoy an included fish lunch. This afternoon we embark on an included cruise on the Bosphorus. We board the boat at Sariyer, a charming fishing village where the Bosphorus meets the Black Sea, and enjoy a perfect vantage point to see the Sultan\u2019s palaces, Rumeli Fortress, the mansions and modern villas forming the elegant part of the city.",
                  "fontSize": 11,
                  "fontName": "MHPMDP\u002BHelveticaNeue",
                  "color": "#221F1F",
                  "boundingBox": {
                    "left": 212.3,
                    "top": 390.3,
                    "width": 345.6,
                    "height": 94.9
                  },
                  "htmlTag": "",
                  "htmlContainerPath": "",
                  "cssClasses": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": "p2-e48",
                  "text": "Day 4",
                  "fontSize": 11,
                  "fontName": "MHPMCN\u002BHelveticaNeue-Medium",
                  "color": "#16549D",
                  "boundingBox": {
                    "left": 212.3,
                    "top": 286.8,
                    "width": 28.3,
                    "height": 7.9
                  },
                  "htmlTag": "",
                  "htmlContainerPath": "",
                  "cssClasses": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": "p2-e49",
                  "text": "This morning we visit the Church of St Saviour in Chora, dating back to the 11th century and home to a fine selection of Byzantine mosaics and frescoes. We continue to the S\u00FCleymaniye Mosque. One of the grandest and most beautiful of the Ottoman mosques, it crowns one of Istanbul\u0027s seven hills and dominates the Golden Horn providing a landmark for the entire city. Our guide then accompanies us to the Grand Bazaar of Istanbul. With 60 alleyways and 3,000 shops, it is the oldest and largest in the world. The bazaar was established by Mehmet II shortly after his conquest of the city in 1453. Our day concludes with a visit to the Spice Bazaar. The bazaar came to specialise in spices from the Orient, taking advantage of Istanbul\u2019s site on the trade route between the East (where most spices are grown) and Europe.",
                  "fontSize": 11,
                  "fontName": "MHPMDP\u002BHelveticaNeue",
                  "color": "#221F1F",
                  "boundingBox": {
                    "left": 212.3,
                    "top": 276.1,
                    "width": 345.4,
                    "height": 138.4
                  },
                  "htmlTag": "",
                  "htmlContainerPath": "",
                  "cssClasses": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": "p2-e50",
                  "text": "Day 5",
                  "fontSize": 11,
                  "fontName": "MHPMCN\u002BHelveticaNeue-Medium",
                  "color": "#16549D",
                  "boundingBox": {
                    "left": 212.3,
                    "top": 129.1,
                    "width": 28.3,
                    "height": 7.9
                  },
                  "htmlTag": "",
                  "htmlContainerPath": "",
                  "cssClasses": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": "p2-e51",
                  "text": "After spending the morning at leisure in Istanbul, we return to Istanbul Airport for our direct scheduled Turkish Airlines back to our allocated London airport. We then continue by private coach back to our original pick up points.",
                  "fontSize": 11,
                  "fontName": "MHPMDP\u002BHelveticaNeue",
                  "color": "#221F1F",
                  "boundingBox": {
                    "left": 212.3,
                    "top": 118.3,
                    "width": 342.1,
                    "height": 40.5
                  },
                  "htmlTag": "",
                  "htmlContainerPath": "",
                  "cssClasses": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": "p2-e52",
                  "text": "NB:- Please note we reserve the right to alter the above itinerary if required for operational",
                  "fontSize": 8,
